<div class="page">
  <div class="panel">

    <!-- 1. HERO -->
    <section class="section" id="hero">
      <div class="section-label">Proposal · Fishnook × The Salt Lick Denver</div>
      <h1 class="heading_h1">Monthly Creative Production for Fishnook</h1>
      <div class="accent-bar"></div>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Built for the testing cadence you're running. Shot for paid first, with usable footage for organic as part of the package.</p>
      <p class="body-text">Jared&mdash; here's the proposal based on our call. With 30 brands and 250+ products running through one storefront, your creative needs to be genuinely different from piece to piece for Andromeda to do its job. Changing hooks on the same video doesn't move the needle like it used to. What moves it now is concept-level variety&mdash; different formats, different angles, different production approaches.</p>
      <p class="body-text">Your media agency keeps running campaigns, targeting, and budgets. We handle creative production, upload the finished assets to your ad account, and pull the performance data to shape what we shoot next month.</p>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider">

    <!-- 2. INVESTMENT -->
    <section class="section" id="investment">
      <div class="section-label">Investment</div>
      <h2 class="heading_h2">Two Options</h2>
      <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">Both tiers work the same way. The difference is shoot days, number of concepts, and how much strategy work we do around the production.</p>

      <div class="tiers-grid">

        <!-- STARTER TIER -->
        <div class="tier-card">
          <span class="tier-tag starter">Starter</span>
          <div class="tier-name">Starter</div>
          <div class="tier-description">One shoot day a month, six videos, and the fundamentals.</div>
          <div class="tier-price-row">
            <span class="tier-price">$4,000</span>
            <span class="tier-cadence">/ month</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="tier-summary-list">
            <li>1 shoot day per month</li>
            <li>6 videos</li>
            <li>4 static ad units</li>
            <li>Color-graded footage library</li>
            <li>Scripts &amp; pre-production</li>
            <li>Monthly performance review</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- GROWTH TIER (FEATURED) -->
        <div class="tier-card featured">
          <span class="tier-badge">Recommended</span>
          <span class="tier-tag growth">Growth</span>
          <div class="tier-name">Growth</div>
          <div class="tier-description">Two shoot days a month, twelve videos, a monthly strategy call, and an organic pipeline from content that fits warm audiences better.</div>
          <div class="tier-price-row">
            <span class="tier-price">$7,000</span>
            <span class="tier-cadence">/ month</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="tier-summary-list">
            <li>2 shoot days per month</li>
            <li>12 videos</li>
            <li>Up to 8 static ad units</li>
            <li>Organic pipeline from warm-audience content</li>
            <li>Color-graded footage library</li>
            <li>Scripts &amp; pre-production</li>
            <li>Monthly performance review + strategy call</li>
            <li>Landing page consultation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="investment-footnotes">
        <p><strong>Month 1 billing:</strong> Paid in full when you sign, covering onboarding, pre-production, and the first production cycle (about 4&ndash;5 weeks). Every month after that is billed when the previous cycle's creative is delivered.</p>
        <p><strong>Commitment:</strong> Month-to-month. No long-term contract.</p>
        <p><strong>Travel:</strong> All Denver metro production (including Commerce City) is included. Shoots outside the metro get quoted separately.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider">

    <!-- 3. WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
    <section class="section" id="whats-included">
      <div class="section-label">What's Included</div>
      <h2 class="heading_h2">What's in Every Tier</h2>
      <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">Both tiers include the same four pieces. The tier you pick changes the volume.</p>

      <div class="services-grid">

        <div class="deliverable-card">
          <span class="deliverable-tag core">Strategy</span>
          <h3 class="heading_h3">Pre-Production &amp; Scripts</h3>
          <p class="body-text">Every concept gets a brief, a script, and a shot list. Scripts go out for approval before we shoot. Performance data from the previous month feeds into the next month's scripts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="deliverable-card">
          <span class="deliverable-tag">Production</span>
          <h3 class="heading_h3">Video Production &amp; Edit</h3>
          <p class="body-text">Shot at your Commerce City warehouse. A mix of hero videos (fully produced, multi-angle) and UGC-style pieces (single-angle, recipe-forward). Every video is its own creative direction. Delivered in vertical and square for Feed, Reels, and Stories.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="deliverable-card">
